translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぐがー……ぐがー……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Guga... guga...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やれやれ、これじゃただの子守だね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Good grief, this is just babysitting, isn't it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まあ、まんざらじゃないんだけどさ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, it's not entirely unpleasant though.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひゃひゃひゃひゃ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hyahahahaha!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺に逆らう奴は真っ二つだぜ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Anyone who goes against me gets cut in half!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なに？　エレナちゃんに苦情が来てるだと？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What? You're saying there's a complaint about Elena-chan?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ええ、その通りです」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, exactly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「元々、山賊団ですからね……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Originally, they're a band of mountain bandits...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 普通の兵士達とのトラブルが相次ぎ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Troubles with regular soldiers have been happening one after another...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「このままでは放逐も考えねばなりません」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At this rate, we might have to consider expulsion.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それは駄目だ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That must not happen.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エレナちゃんは可愛いからな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Because Elena-chan is cute.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……そう仰るなら、注意して下さい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...If you say so, then please warn them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう不満を抑えておくのも限界に……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's almost at the limit where they can hold back their dissatisfaction...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うむうむ、今度やっとこう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, hmm, I'll take care of it this time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「今すぐ行く！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll go right now!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まったく、クリームちゃんめ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Really, that Cream-chan,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最近ノリがオカンみたいになってる気が……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lately, she feels like she's taken on a motherly vibe...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お、いたいた」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, there you are.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あーーーーーん？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Aaaaaan?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺達に苦情だぁ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A complaint against us?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おう、そうなんだが……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yeah, that's right, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それより、お前ら集まって何してる……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: More importantly, what are you all gathered here doing...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うへっ、酒くさっ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh, you all smell like alcohol.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひゃひゃひゃひゃひゃ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hyahahahahaha!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 見て分かんねぇのかよ、酒盛りだよ、酒盛り！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Can't you see? We're having a drinking party, a drinking party!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「こんな昼間から……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Drinking like this in the middle of the day...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なるほど、こりゃ怒られるわけだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I see, no wonder you're getting scolded.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お前ら兵士達とトラブルばかり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They say you guys keep causing trouble with the soldiers.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 起こしてるそうではないか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Isn't that right?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「けーーーーーーーっ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Heh-ooooh!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それで注意に来たってのかよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So you came to warn us because of that?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ひゃひゃひゃ、王様っても、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hyahaha, even a king,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やってるこたお役所みてぇだな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Feels like just some government office business.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「王様違う、総統閣下だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Not king, Supreme Commander.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「王様もそーとーかっかも大して変わんねぇだろ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A king or a supreme commander, they're not all that different!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さすがっす、エレナの姐御！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As expected of Elena's big sister!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いよっ、器がデカイ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yeah, what a magnanimous person!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺達、一生ついていきまーす！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll follow you for life!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お前らもエレナを甘やかすんじゃない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You guys, don't spoil Elena either.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なーーーんか、下らねぇこと考えてんなぁ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow, you guys are thinking about stupid things.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はあ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺ぁ、テメェなんか大ッッッ嫌ぇだけどよ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I totally hate you,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: テメェのやること自体は好きだぜ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But I like what you do.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やることメチャクチャで、バカ中のバカで、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What you do is total chaos, stupid among the stupid,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: バカやることに命を賭けた馬鹿野郎は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A dumbass who bets his life on doing stupid things,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: フラワー番地強盗団は大好きだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I love the Flower District Robber Gang!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「せいぜいテメェには、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: More than anything, I want you to

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この世界をメッチャクチャにして欲しいね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: mess this world up big time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だってのに、なんだそのツラ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And yet, what's with that face?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やってるこたお役所みてぇだな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Feels like just some government office business.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「王様違う、総統閣下だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Not king, Supreme Commander.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「王様もそーとーかっかも大して変わんねぇだろ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A king or a supreme commander, they're not all that different!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さすがっす、エレナの姐御！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As expected of Elena's big sister!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いよっ、器がデカイ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yeah, what a magnanimous person!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺達、一生ついていきまーす！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll follow you for life!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お前らもエレナを甘やかすんじゃない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You guys, don't spoil Elena either.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なーーーんか、下らねぇこと考えてんなぁ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow, you guys are thinking about stupid things.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はあ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺ぁ、テメェなんか大ッッッ嫌ぇだけどよ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I totally hate you,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: テメェのやること自体は好きだぜ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But I like what you do.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やることメチャクチャで、バカ中のバカで、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What you do is total chaos, stupid among the stupid,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: バカやることに命を賭けた馬鹿野郎は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A dumbass who bets his life on doing stupid things,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: フラワー番地強盗団は大好きだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I love the Flower District Robber Gang!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「せいぜいテメェには、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: More than anything, I want you to

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この世界をメッチャクチャにして欲しいね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: mess this world up big time.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だってのに、なんだそのツラ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And yet, what's with that face?
